28:58.086 --> 28:59.838
Yeah, I know, I know.

29:00.464 --> 29:02.341
I was thinking of "Marc."

29:02.591 --> 29:04.009
What do you think?

29:04.510 --> 29:06.678
Is that with a "c" or a "k"?

29:10.348 --> 29:11.974
My name is with...

29:13.101 --> 29:14.227
a "k."

29:15.269 --> 29:18.397
So I was thinking
maybe my band could be with a "c"...

29:18.981 --> 29:21.609
so that way it's a psychedelic trip thing.

29:22.360 --> 29:24.903
Always play with their minds.

29:32.494 --> 29:33.995
Nice selection.

29:37.958 --> 29:41.001
- Help you with anything?
- No, I'm all right.

29:41.085 --> 29:43.337
- You like music?
- Yeah.

29:43.879 --> 29:45.089
Me, too.

29:45.965 --> 29:48.133
