31:17.967 --> 31:20.470
- He cut it too short.
- No, it's fine. Really.

31:20.553 --> 31:22.013
It's fabulous.

31:24.724 --> 31:25.808
Oh, God.

31:25.975 --> 31:27.310
Look at this place!

31:27.435 --> 31:30.187
There is no gig too small, all right?

31:30.228 --> 31:33.815
Middle America buys your records.
We got a lot of fans waiting.

31:35.567 --> 31:38.737
This is Joe Reaves
from the Empire Records store.

31:39.196 --> 31:41.907
