didn't they?

32:18.941 --> 32:23.237
I think Music Town is actually torn
on the revealing garment issue.

32:23.654 --> 32:24.989
I think so.

32:25.239 --> 32:26.740
Revealing clothing.

32:41.796 --> 32:43.256
Gina, would you get dressed.

32:45.008 --> 32:46.175
Turn that down.

32:46.259 --> 32:48.343
A.J., up on the roof. Fix the sign.

32:48.635 --> 32:50.095
Take the photograph.

32:51.680 --> 32:54.141
Music Town. I can handle Music Town.

33:00.689 --> 33:03.441
Welcome to Music Town.
May I service you?

33:06.110 --> 33:07.069
Gina...

33:07.278 --> 33:09.196
