33:09.989 --> 33:11.282
You must be Joe Reaves.

33:11.365 --> 33:12.992
You must be Jane.

33:13.159 --> 33:14.535
Me, Joe. You, Jane.

33:14.618 --> 33:15.953
Shut up, Warren.

33:16.954 --> 33:19.205
- This is Rex Manning.
- Pleased to meet you.

33:19.289 --> 33:21.124
We all love the new album.

33:21.333 --> 33:22.208
Good for you.

33:22.334 --> 33:23.793
What's he doing here?

33:24.836 --> 33:26.463
Let me introduce you.

33:26.504 --> 33:29.340
This is Gina. This is Corey.

33:29.507 --> 33:30.800
Lucas, A.J...

33:30.842 --> 33:32.761
and Warren.

33:33.635 --> 33:35.846
I'm Rex. Great to be here.

33:35.929 --> 33:37.598
I have all...

33:37.848 --> 33:39.141
your albums.

33:39.850 --> 33:42.186
That's terrific, Corey. Thanks.

33:42.269 --> 33:43.979
What happened to your hair?

33:46.523 --> 33:50.276
The stylist, if you can call him that,
got carried away. No biggie.

33:50.485 --> 33:51.611
Looks good.

33:51.694 --> 33:52.570
See, he likes it?

33:52.653 --> 33:54.363
I like it.

33:55.031 --> 33:55.823
Great.

33:55.865 --> 33:57.241
Let's go to work.

33:58.159 --> 33:59.160
Higher.

34:14.174 --> 34:15.759
That was fabulous, Warren, thank you.

34:21.514 --> 34:22.848
Women.

34:24.891 --> 34:26.726
I still don't like my hair.

34:26.976 --> 34:28.646
Just try to smile.

34:31.232 --> 34:32.650
I don't like the chair.

34:32.733 --> 34:34.360
What do you mean,
