34:53.001 --> 34:54.837
- What's your name?
- Kathy.

34:55.045 --> 34:56.922
K-A-T-H-Y.

34:58.132 --> 35:01.385
I've seen every episode of The Family Way.

35:01.885 --> 35:03.595
You were my favorite singer
in high school.

35:06.056 --> 35:07.974
Who's your favorite singer now?

35:08.391 --> 35:10.226
You! It's still you!

35:38.919 --> 35:40.796
There're so many babes out there!

35:40.921 --> 35:44.008
I've got to get Rex some water
because Rex is very thirsty.

35:44.967 --> 35:46.719
Make sure it's bottled water.

35:49.013 --> 35:51.056
Who's your favorite singer?

35:51.432 --> 35:52.308
Axl.

35:53.349 --> 35:56.311
If Axl Rose was driving
down the highway...

35:56.478 --> 35:59.772
and saw Rex Manning stranded
on the side of the road...

35:59.939 --> 36:02.108
would Axl Rose stop and help him?

36:05.945 --> 36:07.780
Does Axl have a jack?

36:08.156 --> 36:13.202
No way, man! Axl would spin the wheel,
take aim, pound on the gas...

36:14.620 --> 36:16.497
and take that sucker out!

36:20.000 --> 36:22.920
Warren! Where do you get
this hostility from?

36:35.306 --> 36:37.141
Who glued these quarters down?

36:37.308 --> 36:38.059
I did.

36:38.142 --> 36:40.101
What the hell for, man?

36:40.644 --> 36:43.605
I don't feel that I need
to explain my art to you.

36:46.858 --> 36:48.401
Look what you took.

36:48.693 --> 36:49.778
Rap...

36:50.362 --> 36:51.571
...metal...

36:52.113 --> 36:53.323
...rap...

36:53.907 --> 36:54.991
...metal...

36:55.866 --> 36:57.368
...Whitney Houston.

36:57.701 --> 36:59.161
It's for my girlfriend, okay.

36:59.203 --> 37:00.496
Sure it is.

37:00.663 --> 37:03.332
Someone like you needs
to diminish their criminal impulses...

37:03.374 --> 37:06.293
not magnify them.

37:06.460 --> 37:08.379
Maybe some jazz or classical.

37:08.879 --> 37:10.464
Maybe you bite me.

37:11.839 --> 37:13.299
Do any of you...

37:13.383 --> 37:15.134
like Rex Manning's new record?

37:20.431 --> 37:23.184
Dance Party, U.S.A.
Teenybopper type of shit.

37:24.727 --> 37:27.354
