37:28.230 --> 37:32.234
Did you compare the percentage
of teenage male Rex Manning fans...

37:32.317 --> 37:35.696
to the incidents of homosexuality
among teenage males?

37:36.697 --> 37:37.656
No.

37:40.701 --> 37:42.160
