it's my mom's.

37:49.917 --> 37:52.086
She loves you.
I've never even heard of you.

37:54.422 --> 37:56.924
Does your mother
still have her own teeth?

37:57.216 --> 37:58.383
Forget it.

37:58.675 --> 38:00.010
Cool hair.

38:17.818 --> 38:18.652
Berko.

38:18.736 --> 38:20.946
Lucas, heard a story about you.

38:21.030 --> 38:22.406
Really? Which one?

38:22.573 --> 38:24.116
The one where you stole $9,000...

38:25.326 --> 38:26.994
went to Atlantic City...

38:27.077 --> 38:29.038
and there's a contract out on you.

38:29.787 --> 38:32.206
Has anyone seen Debra today?

38:32.457 --> 38:33.916
We saw her.

38:34.000 --> 38:35.585
She shaved her head...

38:35.710 --> 38:37.837
and has a bandage on her wrist.

38:38.338 --> 38:39.422
Really?

38:39.464 --> 38:40.590
Really.

38:42.633 --> 38:43.801
Who are you?

38:44.177 --> 38:45.302
I'm Jane.

38:47.179 --> 38:49.014
I work for Rex Manning.

38:56.772 --> 38:58.440
You think that's funny?

39:02.943 --> 39:04.487
If you'll excuse me.

39:05.446 --> 39:07.073
You're quitting? You can't quit.

39:07.156 --> 39:09.450
It's not them. It's Rex.

39:09.742 --> 39:11.619
You know, I don't even like his music.

39:11.660 --> 39:13.996
Come on Jane. You gotta stay.

39:14.121 --> 39:15.289
I need a change of scenery.

39:15.331 --> 39:17.499
Honey, come on. You can't do it to...

39:20.502 --> 39:22.962
I can't believe it. She quit.

41:01.638 --> 41:04.892
Excuse me, ladies.
Less shimmy, more selling. Thanks.

41:05.433 --> 41:07.226
Guess who's here.

41:09.103 --> 41:11.647
How are you?
Mitchell Beck. I own this place.

41:11.731 --> 41:13.816
Good to meet you. You have a nice store.

41:13.900 --> 41:17.278
Nice of you to say.
You should have seen it originally.

41:17.487 --> 41:19.280
Beck's Bath and Bidet.

41:19.363 --> 41:22.699
Bathroom fixtures emporium.
My grandfather started it.

41:22.949 --> 41:27.496
It was my beatnik father
who turned it into a record store.
I tell you, if I was selling toilets today

41:28.079 --> 41:29.581
I'd be a rich man.

41:30.957 --> 41:33.001
What's with you?
You're sweating like a pig.

41:33.084 --> 41:34.794
It's nice to see you, too.

41:35.545 --> 41:38.214
Joe, come on.
Is this the way we treat Mr. Manning?

41:38.297 --> 41:40.800
- Where's the fresh fruit? Champagne?
- That's not necessary, thank you.

41:40.883 --> 41:42.218
No, no, please.

41:42.301 --> 41:44.345
- He's a big star.
- Big, huge star. Big.

41:44.470 --> 41:45.971
Let's get him something.

41:48.724 --> 41:52.769
I'm going to the bank.
Give me last night's deposit.

41:52.852 --> 41:53.895
I wanna make sure it gets there this time.
- I'll take care of it.

41:53.978 --> 41:55.855
No, you're a busy man, let me.

41:57.524 --> 41:59.025
I said I'll handle it.

42:07.200 --> 42:08.867
Mitch, have you met Warren?

42:08.951 --> 42:10.035
Who're you?

42:10.118 --> 42:12.287
Lucas. I work here.

42:13.121 --> 42:14.957
Have you met Warren?

42:15.123 --> 42:17.292
I wanted to talk to you about him.

42:17.459 --> 42:19.711
Young Warren came into the store today...

42:19.795 --> 42:23.339
and put on a little demonstration
for all the store employees.

42:23.464 --> 42:26.801
Very motivational.
It was inspiring, actually.

42:26.968 --> 42:30.263
He just made quite an impression
on everybody.

42:30.471 --> 42:32.932
I'm intrigued. I'm spellbound.

42:34.267 --> 42:37.103
That wasn't so hard, was it? Thank you.

42:53.994 --> 42:55.452
Like your hair.

43:00.499 --> 43:01.709
Are you okay?

43:01.834 --> 43:03.711
Why do you care?
You didn't care last night.

43:03.794 --> 43:05.129
Yes, I did.

43:06.630 --> 43:09.216
Look, this isn't about you, okay?

43:09.757 --> 43:13.511
I got home last night and I thought
about everything that had happened...

43:14.012 --> 43:16.598
and what happened the night before that...

43:16.681 --> 43:19.851
and the week before that
and the year before that.

43:19.934 --> 43:24.188
The only thing that was different was
something else was making me feel shitty.

43:24.355 --> 43:26.023
I'm trying to say I'm sorry.

43:26.106 --> 43:28.483
I just said, this wasn't about you.

43:30.611 --> 43:33.989
You didn't do anything wrong.
I'm screwed up.

43:34.072 --> 43:35.198
We're all screwed up.

43:35.282 --> 43:37.034
Don't touch me right now.

43:37.367 --> 43:40.287
I just want you to get up
and I want you to walk away.

43:48.377 --> 43:49.462
Corey...

43:50.129 --> 43:53.382
...I've got to tell you something.
It's about how I feel about you.

43:56.760 --> 43:58.720
I really, really...

44:01.890 --> 44:03.475
Oh, God...

44:03.934 --> 44:06.645
You know that feeling you get
when you get out of a hot bath?

44:06.895 --> 44:09.731
You just feel really refreshed and nice.

44:10.106 --> 44:12.858
Well, you make me feel like...
You make me feel like a bath?

44:12.983 --> 44:16.445
You're like vanilla ice cream.
French vanilla ice cream.

45:33.434 --> 45:34.768
This is bullshit!

45:34.893 --> 45:38.522
The long arm of the law
has embraced our dear friend Warren.

45:39.189 --> 45:41.608
I'm Joe Reaves, manager.
Everything okay?

45:41.692 --> 45:43.986
Joe, tell them what he did.

45:44.028 --> 45:46.529
- You need a statement?
- No, Mr. Lucas gave us one.

45:46.571 --> 45:49.741
Mr. Lucas over there. He took $9,000!

45:50.450 --> 45:52.910
- That's enough.
- I only took a couple of CDs.

45:53.536 --> 45:54.579
Come on!

45:54.871 --> 45:57.623
- Lucas, I thought you were my friend.
- Don't let the man get you down.

45:57.707 --> 45:59.917
I don't wanna see you back in the store.

46:00.001 --> 46:02.836
I'm gonna get you!
I'm not playing this time!

46:02.961 --> 46:05.380
I'll be back and you'll be sorry!

46:05.505 --> 46:07.424
You'll hang for this!

46:08.175 --> 46:09.926
"You'll be sorry!"

46:10.135 --> 46:11.803
I'm already sorry.

46:31.322 --> 46:34.407
Hi. I'm just doing
the quarterly income tax returns.

46:34.491 --> 46:35.867
Almost done.

46:40.163 --> 46:41.831
Look, Deb...

46:43.917 --> 46:46.086
if you need to talk about anything...

46:47.420 --> 46:49.213
You gonna fix me, Joe?

46:51.090 --> 46:52.883
Fix me. I'll listen.

46:53.759 --> 46:55.719
I didn't mean that.

46:55.928 --> 46:57.888
Should I call your mother or something?

46:59.431 --> 47:02.518
Great. You know, if you find her,
could you give me her number?

47:02.601 --> 47:05.061
Because I'd like to talk to her myself.

47:07.730 --> 47:09.690
I know you didn't mean anything.

47:14.737 --> 47:16.364
You're doing a good job.

47:25.455 --> 47:27.124
I feel a lot better.

47:31.128 --> 47:32.170
Dear.

47:32.295 --> 47:34.005
Best boss in the world.

47:34.089 --> 47:36.048
Can I bring Rex his lunch?

47:36.257 --> 47:37.800
Berko's taking him his lunch.

47:38.467 --> 47:42.972
You know that Berko's going to insult him
right to his face. It's not a good idea.

47:43.138 --> 47:46.767
I don't care if Berko sticks an M-80
up his butt and lights it.

47:46.851 --> 47:49.645
I hope he sticks one up mine.
It'd be an improvement.

47:50.937 --> 47:53.022
I have to bring Rex his lunch.

47:53.148 --> 47:54.440
Berko is.

47:54.732 --> 47:57.485
Joe, I need to bring him his lunch.

47:58.570 --> 47:59.821
Berko is.

48:00.155 --> 48:02.782
I'm bringing Rex his lunch!

48:04.826 --> 48:05.951
All right.

48:07.661 --> 48:08.996
Thanks, Joe.

48:09.830 --> 48:11.582
Thanks a lot.

48:49.868 --> 48:51.328
Guava food groups.

48:51.494 --> 48:52.912
Good-bye, Mark.

48:56.207 --> 48:58.584
Well, this looks very elegant.

49:01.378 --> 49:05.174
Boy, talking to all those women
can make you work up an appetite.

49:07.551 --> 49:08.801
I'll bet it does.

49:10.303 --> 49:12.972
I got everything. I'm all set. Thank you.

49:13.097 --> 49:14.515
So am I.

49:20.230 --> 49:24.441
I can't help but notice
you sitting there staring at me.

49:24.691 --> 49:28.820
I was thinking how I used to imagine marrying
you when you were on The Family Way.

49:30.364 --> 49:31.573
Marrying me?

49:31.657 --> 49:33.533
You must've been a baby back then.

49:39.081 --> 49:40.831
I'm not a baby now.

49:44.001 --> 49:45.711
You're a sweet girl.

49:48.881 --> 49:51.050
I'm not as sweet as you think.

49:51.884 --> 49:53.219
How old are you?

49:54.262 --> 49:55.720
Old enough.

50:02.102 --> 50:03.895
Sure you want to do this?

50:04.020 --> 50:05.438
Definitely.

50:12.945 --> 50:14.405
Rock and roll.

50:45.559 --> 50:46.685
Why?

50:47.978 --> 50:49.396
