50:49.646 --> 50:51.898
I'm fixing the sign.
What are you doing here?

50:51.982 --> 50:53.567
Taking a break.

50:54.151 --> 50:56.486
It's so weird that you just came up here.

50:56.570 --> 50:57.945
I have to tell you something.

50:58.321 --> 50:59.113
Not now, please. Please A.J., no.

50:59.155 --> 51:00.322
No, it has to be now.

51:00.406 --> 51:01.657
No, it has to be now.

51:01.741 --> 51:05.453
You remember that really horrible day
when Mark set off the store alarm...

51:05.661 --> 51:08.497
and Gina got dumped by Dennis
and cried all day...

51:08.581 --> 51:11.584
and I drew the picture of him
and Lucas made a voodoo doll...

51:11.667 --> 51:13.460
and you wore that skirt that I hate?

51:13.501 --> 51:14.669
What skirt?

51:15.045 --> 51:17.422
- The one with the flowers.
- The blue skirt?

51:17.505 --> 51:19.174
Yeah, the blue one.

51:19.341 --> 51:20.633
I hate that skirt.

51:21.051 --> 51:24.637
It's good that I hate that skirt. Listen.

51:24.929 --> 51:28.307
Listen to me.
That skirt made me realize that...

51:29.183 --> 51:31.977
if I can love her in that skirt,
then this must really be it.

51:33.062 --> 51:35.230
Corey, I love you.

51:37.524 --> 51:38.484
What?

51:39.693 --> 51:41.445
I'm in love with you.

51:42.362 --> 51:44.697
I mean, I've been in love with you.

51:44.781 --> 51:47.492
Wow, please, not now. Please, A.J.

51:48.201 --> 51:52.538
Please don't do this right now.
I'm sorry, but I can't handle this right now.

51:52.914 --> 51:55.958
Are you telling me
you could handle it some other time?

51:56.042 --> 51:57.001
Look...

51:57.210 --> 52:00.212
I just threw myself at Rex Manning, okay?

52:00.462 --> 52:03.006
And made a total fool of myself.

52:03.423 --> 52:04.382
You what?

52:04.466 --> 52:07.010
Yes, and I'm not ready for this, okay?

52:07.761 --> 52:09.054
I'm sorry.

52:13.058 --> 52:15.518
I'm sorry, I just want to be alone, okay?

52:15.851 --> 52:17.144
Yeah, okay.

52:21.482 --> 52:23.359
Forget I said anything, okay?

52:23.567 --> 52:26.529
Just forget it. I didn't say anything.
Nothing happened.

52:48.757 --> 52:49.883
Forget about Rex.

52:49.925 --> 52:52.761
- We'll get you another guy.
- I don't want another guy. I'm not like you.

52:52.845 --> 52:56.765
I don't need one.
Why do you try and make me like you?

52:57.349 --> 52:58.892
What do you mean?

53:03.354 --> 53:06.899
I'm not like you. I don't need to do
what you do all the time.

53:07.775 --> 53:09.360
Okay. I see.

53:09.527 --> 53:12.363
